{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/logDomain"},"metadata":{"title":"logDomain","externalID":"s:4GLib9logDomainSivp","fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"logDomain"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"var","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"roleHeading":"Global Variable"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"logDomain"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Libraries should define this so that any messages"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which they log can be differentiated from messages from other"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"libraries and application code. But be careful not to define","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"it in any public header files.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Log domains must be unique, and it is recommended that they are the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"application or library name, optionally followed by a hyphen and a sub-domain"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"name. For example, ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"bloatpad"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"bloatpad-io"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If undefined, it defaults to the default "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":" (or ","type":"text"},{"code":"\"\"","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":") log domain; this is","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"not advisable, as it cannot be filtered against using the "},{"code":"G_MESSAGES_DEBUG","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"environment variable."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For example, GTK uses this in its "},{"code":"Makefile.am","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"code":["AM_CPPFLAGS = -DG_LOG_DOMAIN=\\\"Gtk\\\""],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Applications can choose to leave it as the default ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" (or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"\""},{"text":")","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"domain. However, defining the domain offers the same advantages as","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"above.","type":"text"}]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/logdomain"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Defines the log domain. See "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"#log-domains","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/logDomain":{"title":"logDomain","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Defines the log domain. See "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"#log-domains","type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"logDomain","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/logDomain","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/logdomain"},"#log-domains":{"url":"#log-domains","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Log Domains","type":"text"}],"type":"link","title":"Log Domains","identifier":"#log-domains"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","title":"GLib","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/glib","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","type":"topic"}}}